ly.<br><br>HE DIDN'T BELIEVE ME :o (<br><br>Should I have just kept my mouth shut? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/bguild75784.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=lhyra>Lhyra</A> at: 5/6/02 11:38:54 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/udyaan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dyaan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Scowls at you rdy to attack!</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#333333>(5/7/02 10:33:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Invigor is not haste</span><hr size=1> You could have gone one step further and explained that you have the Invigor spell (think we clerics get it before L35) and  since cleric Invigor is a stam buff, you just &quot;assumed&quot; the bard song affected stam also.....maybe it would get him thinking about checking what his song is meant to do. <p>Dyaan Truesite<BR>Level 56 Templar<BR><BR>Hegemony<BR>You can't scare me, I have children!!</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm16.showNextMessage?topicID=5.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm16.emailToFriend?topicID=5.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm16.threadControl?topicID=5.topic